originalText.text: Jeff is the straightest shooter I've encountered through decades of moving up to my current  system.  Not only is his ear acutely tuned  to the vibe that makes analog music so much more satisfying than digital sound, he is a great guy as well.  Thoroughly professional in his transactions, his priority has always been that I'm happy with the choices I've made. With his help, my system now simply disappears, leaving in its place only a musical experience.

originalText.text:
If you love music, you'll love High Water Sound. Jeff is one of the most astute, considerate, and intelligent listeners of both music and customer needs to be found in audio... and far beyond. Moreover, I learned more about audio in the course of listening to music with Jeff than I have over years exploring its possibilities without the benefit of his advice.

High Water Sound helped me build a system matching extremely exacting demands for sound reproduction and pricing, which are often at odds – and did so graciously, with encyclopedic knowledge of recordings and playback components, with every consideration and care for me, his vendors, and others in his industry. His followup and his anticipation of needs alike are both world class, besting the service one finds in even the most rarified of NY contexts for audio systems (and other luxuries).

His audio system is also a joy to hear; it's a true reference. To say I am impressed by High Water Sound is a serious understatement. A+++ highest recommendation.
